---
title: Peri Peri-Glazed Lamb Shoulder with Parmesan Potato Mash & Chilli Lemon Greens
description: A peri peri sauce can go with any meat, and it spruces up this tender lamb shoulder to draw people to your table. The sharp
Parmesan in the mashed potatoes is also an alluring addition, everyone will be in awe.
